<h3>Features</h3>

<ul class="list-disc pl-5">
    <li>
        <h4>Makes use of the News Api to allow users to search for
        recent news articles on specific topics</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
            <li>
                <p>Shows metadata about the articles, including the source,
                title, author, description, and the publish date</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Links to the original article</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        <h4>A friendly user interface</h4>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
            <li>
                <p>No ads or tracking - the site makes money with user subscriptions</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Users that are not subscribed are not allowed searches - only the "trending"
                articles that are on the home page</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Simple search form and list without complex styling and animations</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>
        <h4>Authentication via email and password or Google sign in</h4>
    </li>
    <li>
        <h4>Monthly subscription payments with Stripe</h4>
    </li>
</ul>
